{"tid":455410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇變態伸鹹豬手！女子火大脫衣狂甩豪乳掌嘴","createTime":"2017-11-02T05:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T05:35:54.000Z","uid":120541,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d06b0cb5e4a4ca8d0ad77cfad930571819f99a9","tid":455410,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"事件發生於巴西的里貝朗普雷圖（Ribeirao Preto），一名妙齡女子在路上發傳單發到一半，突然將一名男子壓制在地，引起路人圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n她用腳踩著男子的手，大聲指控男子對她伸出鹹豬手，不過男子反駁，說他只是帶著妻子出來血拼，否認對她性騷擾，女子卻不買帳，火大的脫下藍色上衣塞住他的嘴，身上只剩一件白色背心，大聲咆哮「我厭倦了被視為性對象！奶子就是你想要的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n女子下一秒的舉動令路人驚愕不已，她竟在大庭廣眾之下，直接把白色背心往下拉，露出赤裸的胸部，接著跨坐在男子身上，對他狂甩巴掌。一陣暴打之後，她將男子的雙手固定在地，然後低身將裸胸左右來回甩在男子臉上，讓男子狼狽不堪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4syv40AKQx4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4syv40AKQx4&d=2qj4hJ%2F0yb%2FUxPeMlBt47Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d3a446a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4syv40AKQx4</a>"},{"pid":"ca9a3ba6c8f2852297531e511f585855bdbdd47e","tid":455410,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffed2622bf6d523364171c8a969d402932feeb0","tid":455410,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/130649_c1c81f4fef16cfbf64bf711f8a1fd1a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F130649_c1c81f4fef16cfbf64bf711f8a1fd1a5.jpg&h=2a54974c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/130651_943b9feb7adb903641ea3de7e7b950b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F130651_943b9feb7adb903641ea3de7e7b950b4.png&h=df